- Explain how integrating diverse data makes big data more valuable before analyzing
- Value comes from integrating data sources and analysing them at scale
- bring data in from diverse sources
- managing data and using it programmatically
- discover, access and monitoring data > then modelling and transforming
- integrated data is richer 
- Data integration will:
  * Reduce data complexity
  * Increase data availability
  * Unify your data system
